<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    PATAGONIAN PALACE. The Llao Llao Hotel emerges from a tragic
history as an elite hideaway on the edge of the Andean Mountains.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-CELEBRITY-HIDEAWAY-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f''
financial, ``t'' travel and ``l'' lifestyle.
 &HT;    
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased _ the rate is not
prohibitive _ from New York Times sales representatives ANA PENA in
New York at 212-499-3333 or fax at 212-499-3382; or KARL HORWITZ in
Paris at 47-42-17-11, or fax at 47-42-80-44 or 47-42-18-81; New
York Times Syndicate Sales Executive DEBORAH WEYDERT at
