   Please note that the New York Times News Service report includes
news and features from The Arizona Republic, The Boston Globe, Cox
News Service, The Fort Worth Star-Telegram, Hearst Newspapers, The
Houston Chronicle, The Kansas City Star, The Los Angeles Daily
News, The San Francisco Chronicle, The Seattle Post-Intelligencer,
States News Service and the New York Times Regional Newspapers.
</P>
</TEXT>
