</P>
<P>
   VOICESTREAM-DEUTSCHE-REACT (Undated) _ On the regulatory hurdles
and the political reaction to the VoiceStream-Deutsche Telekom
deal. By Stephen Labaton.
</P>
<P>
   KING-ONLINE-NOVEL (Undated) _ Stephen King began offering
chapters of a previously unpublished novel on his Web site Monday
for a dollar per chapter. By David D. Kirkpatrick.
</P>
<P>
   WTO-ASBESTOS (Geneva) _ A recent ruling by the World Trade
Organization that upholds France's ban of Canadian asbestos imports
has caught the attention of environmentalists and labor-rights
activists, who say it indicates the global trade group may be
growing more sensitive to their concerns. By Elizabeth Olson.
</P>
