   BUSH-CHENEY-OIL (Washington) _ If Texas Gov. George W. Bush
selects Richard Cheney as his running mate, the Republicans might
face criticism that they are offering America ``the Big Oil''
ticket. Democrats could revive questions about Bush's ties to
Harken Energy when it won an exclusive offshore oil-drilling
