number of Internet users explodes worldwide and high-speed lines
proliferate, the network may be reaching the limits of its
capacity. But scientists and businesses are exploring a number of
new technologies they hope will keep the Internet working reliably.
(Glass, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTOS.
