   SUNSHINE SALAD &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Shared by Sue Pearcy, Palmdale) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   1 cup white rice &QL;
</P>
<P>
   1 cup chopped celery &QL;
</P>
<P>
   2 cups cooked ham OR turkey cubes &QL;
</P>
