</P>
<P>
   1 package unflavored gelatin &QL;
</P>
<P>
   1/4 cup water &QL;
</P>
<P>
   2 cups cooked cubed chicken &QL;
</P>
<P>
   3/4 cup chopped celery &QL;
</P>
