<HEADLINE>
AMERICA: LEGISLATE, DON'T LITIGATE, TOBACCO PUNISHMENT  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors...Tobacco-Industry States)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 725-word material from The New York
