</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PUTIN-G8-DREAMIN'-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
RUSSIA'S NEW REALISM ABOUT WHERE ITS REAL INTERESTS LIE  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 775-word material from The New York
Times Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist.
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
