<HEADLINE>
GET READY FOR CAMPAIGN 2000'S UNCONVENTIONAL CONVENTIONS  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Political Editors...975 trimmed; 1,050 uncut)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 975-word (trimmed) material from The
