anti-Castroites charging that  &UR; Janet Reno &LR;  is a lesbian, and
Castroites bringing up the fact that Elian's great-uncle Lazaro
used to hang out with homosexuals.
</P>
<P>
   -- The Chicago Sun Times says that Warner Bros. is negotiating
with  &UR; Sammy Sosa &LR; 's agents about making a film biography of the
slugger, and Sosa is deciding whether to play himself.
</P>
<P>
   -- Wee ones:  &UR; Alex &LR;  and  &UR; Greg Russell  &LR; just had their first
baby &LR; , &LR;  and named him  &UR; William Oliver StoneCold Russell &LR; , the third
name being for wrestler `` &UR; Stone Cold &LR; ''  &UR; Steve Austin &LR; .
