<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-24 22:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1897 &Cx1f; tta-z
u w BC-CLINTON-FUND-RAISING-     07-24 0719
